{"tid":1658750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰爆衝突 國家打吡或移師班拿貝","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T20:35:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cc32cb367d7807b357fa6d2b84e7920113b36415","tid":1658750,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】由於加泰羅尼亞地區近日爆發示威及衝突，西班牙聯賽會要求把今月的國家打吡，由魯營改至班拿貝舉行。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙政府日前重罰於2017年爭取加泰羅尼亞獨立的9名分離組織領袖入獄9至13年，激發支持加泰羅尼亞獨立的多個組織及民眾上街示威，包括效法香港示威者連日堵塞機場。<br />\n<br />\n今季首場國家打吡將於今月26日在巴塞隆拿主場魯營舉行。由於巴塞正正位於加泰羅尼亞地區，所以西班牙聯賽會懼怕比賽被示威影響，已經向西班牙足總要求，改為於皇家馬德里主場班拿貝舉行。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙聯賽會於聲明中表示：「因為特別的形勢已經超出我們的控制範圍內，我們要求西班牙足總可以更改國家打吡的球場至馬德里。」<br />\n<br />\n這個變動相信對皇馬有利，因為在變動後，皇馬便不用連續3場作客，至於巴塞就要於歐聯遠征捷克的布拉格斯拉維亞後，在連續第3場客場出戰國家打吡。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"c163d92eeccea5bff7d9f8ba49abf797225fa435","tid":1658750,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7cffc3c916f64025d98c9fd4f38d38fdafb9c0f3","tid":1658750,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"依家既皇馬<br />\n巴菜作客照炒789球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aab6fd2b5b0b0f50878e73c78c2a6afbf925d1b","tid":1658750,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"由主場變作客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c526ef92c3f8b85cfb10d9ba8a1f46acb662e87","tid":1658750,"uid":58852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7cffc3c916f64025d98c9fd4f38d38fdafb9c0f3","tid":1658750,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"依家既皇馬<br />\n巴菜作客照炒789球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係皇馬主場收皇馬皮應該會對示威者士氣有幫助"},{"pid":"9924da3a7ccbb208b33eda4ad562b4a41bb3402a","tid":1658750,"uid":30751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:54:57.000Z","msg":"全西班牙得兩個球場咩<br />\n點解唔可以用中立場"},{"pid":"84564ed13381f00ad461dfc4dc5401d12d32b3ac","tid":1658750,"uid":103947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"作客變主場咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28271a3b62a7a1089f2cdc8e645912ccb59f04a1","tid":1658750,"uid":62606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"應該同下半季對賽對調主客場，不過皇主場對巴戰績好似差啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447fda9273df89b089c6b40c6a8358cc5deed108","tid":1658750,"uid":266170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9924da3a7ccbb208b33eda4ad562b4a41bb3402a","tid":1658750,"uid":30751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:54:57.000Z","msg":"全西班牙得兩個球場咩<br />\n點解唔可以用中立場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:00:01.000Z","msg":"可能想對調主客場次，下半季畀番巴塞主場對真馬？"},{"pid":"8606642d7411c7da5cfb26e383f9fe31ff103ecf","tid":1658750,"uid":84934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cffc3c916f64025d98c9fd4f38d38fdafb9c0f3","tid":1658750,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"依家既皇馬<br />\n巴菜作客照炒789球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"西甲邊隊第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fcf9988a04f9b653ca